data.description: Check this out, folks! We've got a wonderful home here, sitting pretty on a big 0.3-acre lot. Talk about space to stretch your legs or plenty of room for friends and family to play!  Close to Saufley Field and NAS Pensacola, the home is ideally situated for the go getter who needs to hit the road running every day and situated between two of the area’s best beaches; Pensacola and Perdido Beach. But wait, there's more! And guess what? The whole place got a rewiring makeover with shiny copper wiring. We're talking about upgraded safety and style.  Inside, you'll find fresh wood flooring in the bedrooms and cool tile everywhere else – easy breezy cleaning days!   Now, let's talk garage goals. It's a 2-car wonderland with a cool partition in the middle. You can park your wheels on one side and set up shop or stash your lawnmower on the other. Versatility at its finest!   Hungry? Well, this kitchen's got you covered. It's not just any kitchen; it's an eat-in kitchen! It even includes a fancy formal dining area and a cute little breakfast nook. You'll be brunching like a boss. The kitchen cabinets and new counter tops were updated and remodeled September 2023 so it’s all fresh and new.  And for entertainment value, this home has a large living area for both informal and formal gatherings and those days when you just want to chill movie or TV marathons.  And to give anyone more room for family and friends who come to visit, the home has been remodeled and a 4th bedroom/bonus room added in September 2023. And the living area leads to the backyard where you will enter a large enclosed patio area where you can extend your entertaining gatherings any time of the year and keep an eye on everyone who is playing in the backyard. And the vinyl flooring makes cleaning a breeze. Last but not least, and you'll find a fenced paradise with a detached workshop/shed measuring 16’x12’– perfect for all your DIY dreams!
